  <!-- EN: Phantom Signal -->
  <WNA_Letter_Permaconst>幽灵信号</WNA_Letter_Permaconst>
  <!-- EN: A series of mysterious phantom signals emanated from deep space, echoing across the planet via hidden relay stations scattered throughout this rimworld. \n\nWhelingnorther Alliance's Permaconst Command has initiated another self-maintenance cycle, and its thralls will once again begin their hunt. Direct confrontation is never a good idea; entrusting the enemy to reliable turret defenses is the best course of action. -->
  <WNA_Letter_Permaconst_Desc>一系列神秘的幽灵信号从宇宙深空而来，经由散落在星球各处的隐秘中继站，在星球的各个角落回荡。\n\n威灵会的恒固指令开启了它的又一个自我维护循环，它所操控的傀儡们将再次开始它们的游猎。直接与其交锋绝不是好主意，将敌人交与可靠的炮塔防线处理才是上策。</WNA_Letter_Permaconst_Desc>

